{"tid":660082,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[屌你／繳你／轎嚟]有無巴打識台山話?","createTime":"2018-05-10T11:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T12:02:15.000Z","uid":16839,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"20139c327c309a0c0a72bb72c579d95824286bc3","tid":660082,"uid":16839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:37:00.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今日返學聽到有個細路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :粗口細路<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :另一個細路<br />\n<br />\n粗口細路一路同另一個猜包剪揼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知佢一路講同對面講<br />\n屌你屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你屌你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知佢同我講屌你屌你係台山話嘅恭喜你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話我係台山人點解唔講得台山話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆你個臭街呀 黎到香港仲唔係肯學廣東話都算<br />\n仲要講到明自己唔係香港人唔撚理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無識台山話既巴打可以幫下手睇下係咪真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16fc95229f1ee806273e64d0f566739265dbf5cf","tid":660082,"uid":155910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T11:41:16.000Z","msg":"香港講咩台山話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 番個細路番台山啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.